机构聘用的人员」。这意味着，部分学生党将不再具备报名资格。此举是为引导公众理性「考证」。 此外，《水平测试细则》还明确测试违规情形从原来的 17 种增加至 21 种。对特别严重的违规情形，给予取消当次全部成绩且禁考 5 年。（证券时报）"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/522607989"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I4YeQq4KIhPAsEAMaCDc4NDE2ODI4IKuyz5EGMAA4c0Apcgk1MjI2MDc5ODl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1647666169.9342237", "card_id": "Q_522174196", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "长春本次疫情中你遇到了哪些让你暖心的瞬间？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee2040b532c47182ea0d1af11385bfb5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/522174196"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I4YeQq4KIhPAsEAMaCDc4MzIwNjg5INyEw5EGMAA4LkAqcgk1MjIxNzQxOTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1647666169.9345775", "card_id": "Q_517025011", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 646}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果你明知道不会在一起，还会去表白吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/517025011"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4YeQq4KIhPAsEAMaCDc3MTc2MzE0IIGetZAGMAA4kAVAK3IJNTE3MDI1MDExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1647666169.9348757", "card_id": "Q_512554486", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 131}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何以「你以为重生就能赢吗？记住，我永远都能玩死你」写一个故事?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "这种黑月光疯批美人得设定真的好爱啊"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6f274fc31dbe8df42fcaf94c18249b8f_720w.j