上，美国学校举办模拟奴隶拍卖会早已不是新闻。2017 年，新泽西州两所小学被曝不仅组织模拟奴隶拍卖会，还叫学生制作通缉逃跑奴隶的海报。在当时就激怒了一众家长，引发舆论热议。然而声讨过后，如今美国校园内的种族歧视事件仍然层出不穷。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-931e0a3b2c5a99ac52137d815bf33cd2_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "42 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/522642649"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4YeQq4KIhPAsEAMaCDc4NDI0NTU0ILaL0JEGMCk46gRAMXIJNTIyNjQyNjQ5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新"}